<inglise> It shall be applicable from 3 December 2001. </inglise>
<eesti> Seda kohaldatakse alates 3. detsembrist 2001. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
